      <td align="justify">
      <br>
Fields from the configuration window to connect to data bases: <br>
      <br>
A: List of ODBC controllers for several types of data bases. <br>
B: user name of the data base. <br>
C: Name of the data base. <br>
D: Host name.<br>
E: Password: key to access to the data base.<br>
F: port used for comunicating with the data base. <br>
G: connection button. <br>
H: button to accept the connection. <br>
I: message that indicates the state of the connection. <br>
      <br>
By means of the following window si possible the attribute selection&nbsp;in the data base.<br>



      </td>



    </tr>



